# DropdownTypeahead

Welcome to `DropdownTypeahead` component.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/dropdown-typeahead
```

```tsx
import { DropdownTypeahead } from '@ids-ts/dropdown-typeahead';
```

