## Token Usage

### Color

**container** â€” Container background, border, and surface colors
- `--color-container-background-accent`
- `--color-container-background-accent-active`
- `--color-container-background-accent-focus`

**text** â€” Primary and secondary text colors
- `--color-text-accent`
- `--color-text-complementary`
- `--color-text-disabled`

**action** â€” Interactive element colors and hover/active/focus states
- `--color-action-complementary`
- `--color-action-complementary-active`
- `--color-action-complementary-border`

**input** â€” Input background, border, placeholder, and focus colors
